{"submission_id":"sub_ddf0d150dfe540ad","run_id":"2026-06-22T19-53-05-167Z_285527-b4328df3_ingest_meeting-doc-68641","submitted_at":"2026-06-22T20:03:33.303Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:ddf0d150dfe540ad157f145f4889cea67df6d096d556e8f540767a5ce8770c97","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_68641","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_omny_fare_capping_details","label":"OMNY Weekly Fare Capping Details","raw_text":"• OMNY customers will be automatically upgraded to unlimited rides each weekly period • After 12 full-fare rides each Monday-Sunday, all rides are free • Works with any OMNY-compatible payment method • No OMNY account required • Customers can track progress at omny.info • Eliminates guesswork & financial risk of choosing between weekly unlimited & pay-per-ride options • Encourages infrequent riders to ride more • Encourages OMNY growth","payload":{"claim_text":"OMNY customers will be automatically upgraded to unlimited rides each weekly period. After 12 full-fare rides each Monday-Sunday, all rides are free. Works with any OMNY-compatible payment method. No OMNY account required. Customers can track progress at omny.info. Eliminates guesswork and financial risk of choosing between weekly unlimited and pay-per-ride options. Encourages infrequent riders to ride more. Encourages OMNY growth.","description":"OMNY Weekly Fare Capping details"},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_68641","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_68641#p007_c0002","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_68641/blocks.jsonl","page_number":7,"block_id":"p007_c0002","text_sha256":"sha256:7f7f74759207402c180b505c498b71838cb38f23957607d26f5c5d9758876592","text_source":"raw_text"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
